title: A Summary of the Cars93 Data set
description:
Description
The Cars93.summary data frame has 6 rows and 4 columns
created from information in the Cars93 data set in the Venables 
and Ripley MASS package. Each row corresponds to a different
class of car (e.g. Compact, Large, etc.).
